data.description: FANTASTIC OPPORTUNITY! ALL BRICK RANCH HOME ON A FULL DAYLIGHT BASEMENT minutes away from Downtown East Point, Atlanta Airport, Downtown Atlanta as well as major interstates such as I-75 and I-285. Step into the entry foyer towards the living room and dining room. The ample eat-in kitchen overlooks the breakfast area with access to the outdoor patio. The main level features three bedrooms with two full bathrooms. Additionally, this home offers a FULL DAYLIGHT Basement with two independent entryways. The basement has been reframed and features three additional bedrooms, laundry, two living areas or media rooms/office as well as one full bathroom. The possibilities are endless with the basement floorplan! The HVAC is less than three years old, the roof was recently replaced a year ago along with the gutters, plumbing was replaced less than five years ago to PVC. The backyard was leveled out and the outdoor storage/workshop was built seven months ago! Conveniently located proximate to the Porsche Experience Center, Delta Flight Museum, East Point Farmers Market, Atlanta Zoo among other Performing Arts Centers and Museums! Book your appointment today!
